{"word":"G4057 - περισσῶς - perissōs - per-is-soce' - Exceedingly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περισσῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">perissōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-is-soce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Exceedingly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அதிகமாய், மூர்க்கமாய், அதிகமதிகமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"beyond measure, extraordinarily"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G4053 - περισσός - perissós - per-is-sos'/4053\">G4053</a>; <i>superabundantly:</i> - exceedingly, out of measure, the more.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4050/4050\">G4050</a>, <a href=\"#/G4051/4051\">G4051</a>, <a href=\"#/G4052/4052\">G4052</a>, <a href=\"#/G4053/4053\">G4053</a>, <a href=\"#/G4057/4057\">G4057</a>, <a href=\"#/G5248/5248\">G5248</a>, <a href=\"#/G5249/5249\">G5249</a>"}]}